\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Staff heights can be measured in any unit of length such as inches or centimetres, but a unit of measurement called the \i rastral number\i0  is also in common use.  Rastral numbers correspond to metric units according to the following list:\par
