\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 In multi-page documents, the first page of the document is foot aligned; the last page of the document is head aligned; all other pages are spread. In a one-page document, if the excess exceeds 0, then the page is head aligned, otherwise the page is spread.\par
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\keepn\fi0\sb240\sa0\li0\ri0\f1\fs28\b0\i1\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Pack from Top\par
